1. *Četvoro* ljudi je sedelo za stolom. (*Four* people were sitting at the table.) 
2. Sutra će doći *četvoro* novih učenika u razred. (Tomorrow, *four* new students will come to the class.) 
3. Oni su *četvoro* pobegli iz zatvora. (They *four* escaped from prison.) 
4. *Četvoro* ljudi je bilo povređeno u saobraćajnoj nesreći. (*Four* people were injured in a car accident.) 
5. Mesto ima *četvoro* vrata i veliki prozor. (The place has *four* doors and a large window.) 
6. Ovaj posao zahteva angažovanje *četvoro* radnika. (This job requires hiring *four* workers.) 
7. *Četvoro* dece se igralo u parku. (*Four* children were playing in the park.) 
8. Prevoz je organizovan za *četvoro* putnika. (Transportation is arranged for *four* passengers.) 
9. Bila je to *četvoro*člana porodica koja je živela u maloj kući. (It was a *four*-member family that lived in a small house.) 
10. *Četvoro* osumnjičenih je uhapšeno u vezi sa pljačkom banke. (*Four* suspects have been arrested in connection with a bank robbery.)